  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strengthening the COVID-19 Response in Kinshasa  Through Improved Preparation and Efficiency of the Congolese National Police</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Through this project, IOM aims to strengthen the COVID-19 response in Kinshasa through improved preparation and efficiency of the Congolese National Police (PNC). In particular, this project seeks to improve relations between the police and the population to strengthen compliance with the restrictive measures applicable to the prevention of COVID-19 through capacity building of the police and with the reduction of contamination risk.</narrative>
  </description>
